*genus2reduction-0.3_p8-r1 (22 Aug 2011)

  22 Aug 2011; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  +genus2reduction-0.3_p8-r1.ebuild, +files/genus2reduction-0.3.p8-pari.patch:
  revbump to use pari-2.5. Because it is an executable only it can be used with
  a sage compiled with pari-2.4 

  03 Aug 2011; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  genus2reduction-0.3_p8.ebuild:
  fixing the version of pari used in 0.3_p8

  20 May 2011; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@students.uni-mainz.de>
  genus2reduction-0.3_p8.ebuild:
  Migrate to EAPI 4

  09 Nov 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  -genus2reduction-0.3_p6.ebuild, -files/genus2reduction-0.3.p2.patch:
  remove old

  01 Nov 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  genus2reduction-0.3_p8.ebuild:
  updated SRC_URI

  19 Sep 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  genus2reduction-0.3_p8.ebuild:
  Updated SRC_URI

  18 Aug 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  genus2reduction-0.3_p6.ebuild, genus2reduction-0.3_p8.ebuild:
  Respect LDFLAGS.

